snippet: Xiomara Castro, the left-wing presidential candidate in last week’s elections, has rejected the official results and called on her supporters to march in the streets.
lead_paragraph: Xiomara Castro, the left-wing presidential candidate in last week’s elections, has rejected the official results and called on her supporters to march in the streets.

byline.contributor: Nicholas Phillips reported from Tegucigalpa, and Elisabeth Malkin from Mexico City.
byline.original: By NICHOLAS PHILLIPS and ELISABETH MALKIN
